textBeforeTable: Squads that are currently empty will display as white -- if you wish to join an empty Squad, you can choose the first one marked with white text Players who choose not to join squads will also show up as Blue in the "Not in a Squad” line All occupied Squads will now show up colored blue on the Squad Selection screen Reset Privacy flag from Private to Public when squad drops to 1 player Disable Privacy flag when 1 man squad Change order of options to LEAVE SQUAD, INV A FRIEND, SWITCH TEAM Allow players to join empty Squads alone, thus having 1/4 squad members Removed FIND ME A SQUAD option Quick notes on Squad changes in the Nov 22 update Single sign on from Battlelog to Origin. If you're not logged in to Origin and join a game server, Battlelog will automatically sign you in to Origin in the background and join the game server User Profile and Stats pages on Battlelog can now be accessed without being signed in to Battlelog if you know a user's URL Ability to share your Profile and Stats pages to Facebook, Google+, and Twitter Newly added Battlelog functionality – Share your stats Support for unranked servers. Unranked servers do not report players' scores to Battlelog, but server administrators can freely control all settings Improved team kill kick configuration Anti-stat padding measures taken, disallowing ranked servers to run
